'''阿卜杜拉蒂夫·本·拉希德·扎亚尼'''（{{lang-en|'''Abdullatif bin Rashid Al Zayani'''}}，{{lang-ar|عبد اللطيف بن راشد الزياني}}），是一名[[巴林|巴林]]工程师及退伍中将。2011年4月1日，担任第五任海湾阿拉伯国家合作委员会秘书长<ref name=grc>{{cite web|title=People|url=http://www.grc.net/?frm_system_action=&PK_ID=32770&frm_action=view_people&frm_module=usermanagement&sec=people&sec_type=d&op_lang=en&override=H.E.+Dr.+Abdullatif+Bin+Rashid++Al-Zayani|work=GULF Research Center|accessdate=26 December 2012|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924023535/http://www.grc.net/?frm_system_action=&PK_ID=32770&frm_action=view_people&frm_module=usermanagement&sec=people&sec_type=d&op_lang=en&override=H.E.+Dr.+Abdullatif+Bin+Rashid++Al-Zayani|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==早期生涯==
扎亚尼出生于[[巴林|巴林]][[穆哈拉格|穆哈拉格]]<ref name=grc/>，之后毕业于英国[[桑德赫斯特皇家军事学院|桑德赫斯特皇家军事学院]]<ref name=bna1apr/>，并在苏格兰佩斯进行航天工程学习<ref name=grc/>。1980年，他在美国俄亥俄州道顿的[[美国空军技术学院|美国空军技术学院]]获得物流管理硕士学位<ref name=bna1apr/>。1986年，他在美国[[海军研究生院|海军研究生院]]获得博士学位<ref name=bna1apr/>。1988年，他在堪萨斯州李文渥斯堡领导与指挥训练中心学习，并获得美国陆军授予的荣誉之剑<ref name=bna1apr/>。

==事业==
扎亚尼在巴林国防部门及大学工作。1973年，成为巴林国防军的指挥官<ref name=cemc>{{cite web|title=Speaker Bio|url=http://www.cemc.ae/SpeakerDetails.aspx?id=76&Lid=1|work=CEMC|accessdate=26 December 2012|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505002748/http://www.cemc.ae/portal/en/home.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，2004年6月2日，他结束了在国防部队的职位。之后担任内政部公共安全司令将军<ref name=tra2july>{{cite news|title=Bahrain to host top security forum|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Bahrain+to+host+top+security+forum.-a0180891168|accessdate=11 April 2013|work=Trade Arabia|date=2 July 2008|location=Manama|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505002801/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Bahrain+to+host+top+security+forum.-a0180891168|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，他晋升中将军衔。同年6月10日，担任巴林国防部长顾问<ref name=bna1apr>{{cite news|title=Dr Abdullatif bin Rashid Al Zayani takes over as GCC secretary general|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Dr+Abdullatif+bin+Rashid+Al-Zayani+takes+Over+as+GCC+Secretary...-a0252986757|accessdate=11 April 2013|work=Bahrain News Agency|date=1 April 2011|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505002807/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Dr+Abdullatif+bin+Rashid+Al-Zayani+takes+Over+as+GCC+Secretary...-a0252986757|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bna21june>{{cite news|title=HRH prince Salman receives Zayani|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/HRH+prince+Salman+receives+Zayani.-a0232686317|accessdate=11 April 2013|work=Bahrain News Agency|date=21 June 2010|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505002759/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/HRH+prince+Salman+receives+Zayani.-a0232686317|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，他还在{{le|阿拉伯海湾大学|Arabian Gulf University}}担任讲师、在[[马里兰大学|马里兰大学]]巴林分校担任数学和统计学教授、在{{le|巴林大学|University of Bahrain}}担任定量分析教授<ref name=grc/>。

2011年4月1日，扎亚尼被任命为[[海湾阿拉伯国家合作委员会|海湾阿拉伯国家合作委员会]]委员长<ref name=cemc/>。最初巴林政府提名另一名候选人[[默罕默德·本·易卜拉欣·阿尔·穆塔瓦|默罕默德·本·易卜拉欣·阿尔·穆塔瓦]]<ref name=arabiya27may>{{cite news|title=Saudi Arabia to mediate in Bahrain-Qatar row|url=http://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2010/05/27/109794.html|accessdate=11 April 2013|work=Al Arabiya|date=27 May 2010|agency=Reuters|location=Riyadh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108195205/http://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2010/05/27/109794.html|archive-date=2016-11-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=hab2nov>{{cite news|last=Toumi|first=Habib|title=Bahrain announces new government|url=http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/bahrain/bahrain-announces-new-government-1.705517|accessdate=18 April 2013|newspaper=Gulf News|date=2 November 2010|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209064155/http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/bahrain/bahrain-announces-new-government-1.705517|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但是由于[[卡塔尔|卡塔尔]]的强烈反对，巴林改为提名扎亚尼担任委员长<ref name=gnews28may10>{{cite news|title=Bahrain names Al Zayani as next GCC chief|url=http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/bahrain/bahrain-names-al-zayani-as-next-gcc-chief-1.633562|accessdate=11 April 2013|newspaper=Gulf News|date=28 May 2010|archive-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109090618/http://gulfnews.com/news/gulf/bahrain/bahrain-names-al-zayani-as-next-gcc-chief-1.633562|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=gdn29may>{{cite news|title=Al Zayani is nominated as GCC secretary-general|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Al+Zayani+is+nominated+as+GCC+secretary-general.-a0227681916|accessdate=11 April 2013|newspaper=Gulf Daily News|date=29 May 2010|location=Manama|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505002831/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Al+Zayani+is+nominated+as+GCC+secretary-general.-a0227681916|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以接替离任的[[阿卜杜拉赫曼·本·哈马德·阿蒂亚|阿卜杜拉赫曼·本·哈马德·阿蒂亚]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Qatar to nominate diplomat for Arab League chief|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Qatar+to+nominate+diplomat+for+Arab+League+chief.-a0253248830|accessdate=11 April 2013|newspaper=Daily News Egypt|date=4 April 2011|location=Cairo|archive-date=2020-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200505002817/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Qatar+to+nominate+diplomat+for+Arab+League+chief.-a0253248830|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

